{"tid":395312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民主黨] 張文光 : 政治歸政治，教育歸教育 ! 請各政治力量遠離校園 !","createTime":"2017-09-10T16:25:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-11T14:40:54.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"131676281f4a57a38f67b13968931ae195bbddd8","tid":395312,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170909/s00001/06bf28160643ed4d942237c24927d0c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170909%2Fs00001%2F06bf28160643ed4d942237c24927d0c1.jpg&h=213b5229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局副局長蔡若蓮長子前日離世後，事件再因部分大學校園民主牆，出現相關冒犯言論而擴大。教協前會長及立法會教育界前議員張文光今日表示，在旅途中剛得悉蔡若蓮長子不幸離世消息，他作為一名父親，感到非常難過，但令他震驚的是，教大竟然出現這樣失掉人性的大字報，令他這位已離開教育界多年的人深感悲傷和羞愧。<br />\n<br />\n張文光指出，一個教師應當明白，人間最大的悲痛是喪親之痛，父母最大的悲痛是喪子女之痛，這是人性，不教自明。若未來當老師的人不明白，枉為人師。他希望教大認真處理這張違反人性和師道的大字報，不容在校園出現。<br />\n張文光更希望，在教大最艱難的時刻，懇請各種政治力量遠離校園，讓政治歸政治，教育歸教育，重回日常，處理事宜。他亦向蔡若蓮及其家人致以深切慰問，希望他們保重節哀，將來如有機會，定當親自慰問。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170909/s00001/1504955744666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170909%2Fs00001%2F1504955744666&d=mLtEjXnqUXMZ4wBHwMEEwfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8469cc34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170909%2Fs00001%2F1504955744666&h=3697eaf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170909/s00001/1504955744666</a>"},{"pid":"8b31f68e276b3838f5802fafe3a529b3808aa432","tid":395312,"uid":22858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"得啦 知你忠心乃共啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbea5191cb7b71022922c4f216ea177078ffc10","tid":395312,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"六四班學生又搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72f177fda56d808b553465e6cac5b96675434aa","tid":395312,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T16:28:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>六四班學生又搞搞震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n民主黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f002dc62244e3b4f9b032d3e46e691cf366ae5be","tid":395312,"uid":11890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"蟈殤之柱呢啲政治嘢唔好擺喺校園囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5505b564f1e13dd46ff0a87fbef5e559f04b6b","tid":395312,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:10:58.000Z","msg":"當年又成日叫學聯出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2a88d1fd211531a06b16be4f1bca81440d326a","tid":395312,"uid":8478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當年又成日叫學聯出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學生對民主黨而言只係Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbad633f6089390a77072663d7a50c90de535858","tid":395312,"uid":121085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:51:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當年又成日叫學聯出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n學生對民主黨而言只係Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學生對所有政黨都係棋子<br />\n個個政黨都話學生衝動思想單純<br />\n<br />\n其實學生幾時單純過<br />\n尤其是大學